			<tm id="tm06"/>
			you talk to a robot.
			<tm id="tm07"/>
			It's a different robot than it used to be 
			<tm id="tm08"/>
			because it was a robot for a while and now
			<tm id="tm09"/>
			it's a friendlier one. 
			<tm id="tm10a"/>
			That's how bad the economy is, even robots
			<tm id="tm10b"/>
