			<tm id="tm11a"/>
			The new one is very pleasant, you know,
			<tm id="tm11b"/>
			you say the name and the number and she goes,
			<tm id="tm12"/>
			alright, I'll connect you. 
			<tm id="tm13a"/>
			It's very very happy, 
			<tm id="tm13b"/>
			and I've named her Noreen. 
			<tm id="tm14a"/>
			The problem with Noreen is
			<tm id="tm14b"/>
			that she doesn't understand anything that I say. 
			<tm id="tm15"/>
			Because at first they say 
			<tm id="tm16"/>
			<voice emotion="calm">'city and place, please'</voice>
			<tm id="tm17"/>
			so, well, I say Los Angeles, California. She goes
			<tm id="tm18"/>
			<voice emotion="calm">Did you say Los Vilas, California?</voice>
			<tm id="tm19"/>
			No I didn't say Los Vilas.
			<tm id="tm20"/>
			<voice emotion="calm">Alright, Los Vilas, what listing please?</voice>
			<tm id="tm21"/>
			No, Los Angeles, California!
			<tm id="tm22"/>
			Leslie's pools.
			<tm id="tm23"/>
			I start screaming, you see,
			<tm id="tm24"/>
			it's like talking to your Grandma, it's like 
			<tm id="tm25"/>
			<voice emotion='happy'>'Grandma I got married!',</voice>
			<tm id="tm26"/>
			'Did you say I'm <voice emotion='sad'>getting buried?!'</voice>
			<tm id="tm27a"/>
			It's so frustrating trying to talk to a robot cause no matter how mad you get,
			<tm id="tm27b"/>
			the lady, Noreen, is so calm.
			<tm id="tm28"/>
			I'm having a hard time understanding you, let's try again. 
			<tm id="tm29"/>
			What do you mean let's try again? 
			<tm id="tm30"/>
			And you're finally just like 
			<tm id="tm31"/>
			'I hate you!'
			<tm id="tm32a"/>
			 and that's when they've connected you to a real-life person, who knows that you want Leslie's pools,
			<tm id="tm32b"/>
			 she's in the background listening!
			<tm id="tm33"/>
			And you just think
			<tm id="tm34"/>
			'Are you just listening the whole time? Just back there?
			<tm id="tm35"/>
			 What are you doing?'
			<tm id="tm36"/>
			It's nice when you're a robot, you can't really get mad at the robot or do anything cause it's a robot,
			<tm id="tm37"/>
			so
			<tm id="tm38"/>
			let me recommend something to you.
			<tm id="tm39"/>
			next time you get pulled over by a cop and the cop says.
			<tm id="tm40"/>
			License and registration.
			<tm id="tm41"/>
			you just go
			<tm id="tm42"/>
			I'm sorry, I didn't hear you, did you say dices and hesitation?
			<tm id="tm43"/>
			no, license and registration.
			<tm id="tm44"/>
			I'm sorry, let's try that again. Did you say 
			<tm id="tm45"/>
			rice gives indigestion?' 
